The updated code will now show the typing animation for each item, fade out, and then start typing the next item. The fade-out transition is set to 1 second. If you want to change the fade-out duration, simply adjust the `transition: opacity 1s;` CSS property and the corresponding `setTimeout(() => { ... }, 1000)` in the JavaScript code.

